*|MC_PREVIEW_TEXT|*
Congratulations! You have been selected for Project Soul to be held on October 15th/16th, 2 pm KST (Korea) (Oct 16th) / 6 am BST (Oct 16th) / 10 pm PDT (Oct 15th).

Please Read!

Project Soul is an exclusive, special event test on October 15th/16th: at 2 pm KST (Korea) (Oct 16th) / 6 am BST (Oct 16th) / 10 pm PDT (Oct 15th).

To prepare for the test, please download and install the Scavengers F2P game from Steam. We will provide additional instructions in Discord within the next 24 hours, so please keep an eye out.

Please note: For those who have tested Icebox in the past, this is NOT one of those tests. This is a special in-game entertainment event that the DAQA community has been given an exclusive sneak peek into. You might even run into some stars!

This test is 1 hour long. Testers will be compensated for a total of 1.5 hours time.

Further communication will take place in Discord. If you are not in our Discord server, please join here: discord URL.

Thank you!

REMINDER: We are still looking for testers with PS4, PS5, Xbox One, and Xbox Series S/X, Tuesday, September 7th for a test, starting at 11:00 am EDT / 4:00 pm BST / 12:00 am JST. Please sign up ASAP!

Action Required!

We are still looking for more testers to enroll. If you would like to participate in this test, please do so before tomorrow!

If you have already enrolled for this test from our Discord announcement, please ignore this email!

Quattro 4 test date has been rescheduled.If you already signed up for this test from last week, you will need to do so again.

This test will now take place Tuesday, September 7th, from 11:00 AM to 1:00 PM EDT / 4:00 pm to 6:00 pm BST / 12:00 am to 2:00 am JST).

This is for PS4, PS4 Pro, PS5, Xbox One, and Xbox Series S/X.

IMPORTANT! For PS4/PS4 Pro/PS5/Xbox - You must have a US PS or a US Xbox account to download the title, but you can play on any account you wish.

A PS+ account is NOT needed for this test.

Instructions to set up a US PSN account here.

Instructions to install the US Xbox build here.

This test will be for NA, EU, and Asia.

Testers will be compensated for a total of 3 hours time to account for prep/install and post test reporting activities.

Sign up here: cognitoURL

Please don't complete the form if you cannot attend the test.

Once you have signed up, please keep an eye on our Discord community. Further communication will take place there. If you are not in our Discord server, please reply to this email and we will send you a link to join.

Thank you!

You have been selected to participate in the Project Icebox 8 beta test on 10-14-2021 at 2:00 pm EDT / 7:00 pm BST / 3:00 am JST.
Congratulations! You have been selected as a PC tester for the upcoming Icebox 7 beta test on Thursday, October 14th. The test begins promptly at 2:00 pm EDT / 7:00 pm BST / 3:00 am JST, and will run for 1 hour. You will be compensated for 1.5 hours of time.

All further communication regarding this test will take place in Discord, so please jump on as soon as possible. Further instructions and test survey links will be provided there.

You will be placed in a dedicated test channel. Please take time to carefully read the information provided in the #announcements and #pinned-info channels.

Test and install instructions can be downloaded here: instructionsURL. Please read them thoroughly prior to the test.

It is critical that we have 100% participation in this test so please let your squad leaders know ASAP if unforeseen circumstances arise. Repeat cancellations will be noted.

Thanks!
